---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy" description="Privacy policy for genlau.com.">
  <section class="page-header page-header--plain">
    <p class="kicker">Privacy.txt</p>
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <p><strong>A plain-English note about what this site collects and why.</strong></p>
  </section>

  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-card">
      <p class="legal-card__updated">Last updated May 28, 2026</p>

      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        This is a personal website for writing, projects, and contact information. I do not sell
        personal information, run user accounts, or collect payment details here.
      </p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        This site uses Google Analytics to understand basic traffic patterns, such as page views,
        referral sources, device/browser information, and approximate location. Google may set
        cookies or use similar technologies to provide those measurements.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you email me or contact me through a linked third-party service, I will receive whatever
        information you choose to send. I use that information to respond to you.
      </p>

      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>
        This site links to other websites, including LinkedIn and other places around the web. Their
        privacy practices are separate from mine.
      </p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>
        You can use browser settings or extensions to block cookies, analytics scripts, or other
        tracking technologies. You can also email me if you have a privacy question about this site.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Privacy questions can be sent to
        <a href="mailto:genevievekaryenlau@gmail.com">genevievekaryenlau@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
